title: 10 year gift
body: I still havent gotten my gift from the 10 year thing are they still being handed out?

replies.body: There are a lot of accounts that need gifting, so not everyone has received them yet.  They are still being handed out per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight until this is all done!
Yeah they are going out in waves and they should show up by [9/23.](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/riot-games/announcements/thank-you)
